OL,3,CRugby league great mic'd up for new
OL,4,Cdocumentary
OL,6,FGranada Reports sports correspondent
OL,7,Fspoke to rugby league player, Sam
OL,8,FTomkins, about the documentary.
OL,10,FA new documentary about the life and
OL,11,Fcareer of rugby league great Sam
OL,12,FTomkins is set to premiere in his
OL,13,Fhometown of .
OL,15,FSam, 34, has now retired from playing,
OL,16,Fbut had a glittering career which saw
OL,17,Fhim win three Super League Grand
OL,18,FFinals with in 2010, 2013, and 2018,
OL,19,Fas well as two Challenge Cup finals in
OL,20,F2011 and 2013.
