OL,6,FHe is also a two-time Man of Steel
OL,7,Frecipient - the award for the rugby
OL,8,Fleague footballer of the year -
OL,9,Fearning the title in 2012 and 2021.
OL,11,FSam, a product of the Wigan Warriors
OL,12,Facademy, finished his career as
OL,13,Fcaptain of England national team
OL,14,Fbefore continuing for a final season
OL,15,Fwith Catalans Dragons in the Super
OL,16,FLeague in 2023.
OL,18,FHis final game as a player was on 14
OL,19,FOctober, when he played in Catalans
OL,20,F2023 Grand Final loss against his
OL,21,Fformer club Wigan.
