OL,4,Cdocumentary
OL,6,FIt was during these final games
OL,7,FTomkins agreed to have a microphone
OL,8,Fput on his shirt for a documentary, so
OL,9,Fpeople would be able to hear what is
OL,10,Fgoing through a player's mind.
OL,12,FSam said: "It is exactly what goes on,
OL,13,Fthe good and the bad on the field
OL,14,Fwhich spectators don't get to see.
OL,16,F"They see it from 50 metres away in
OL,17,Fthe stand or on the TV screen, so it
OL,18,Fwas an opportunity to take people
OL,19,Fright into the thick of it."
