OL,6,FWhen asked if he recognises himself
OL,7,Fwhen he watched it back Sam said:
OL,8,F"It's strange, a lot of funny things
OL,9,Fcame out of it because in the heat of
OL,10,Fthe battle you don't know what you're
OL,11,Fsaying.
OL,13,F"Some of things which have come back,
OL,14,Feither that I've said, or the players
OL,15,Faround, a lot of it is quite comical."
OL,17,FSam told ITV News he wanted to do the
OL,18,Fdocumentary to show the "real side"of
OL,19,Frugby league.
