OL,4,Cdocumentary
OL,6,F"We play a very physical sport, it is
OL,7,Fgladiatorial, and one of the main
OL,8,Fthings about this was it being
OL,9,Fauthentic.
OL,11,F"I don't really mind what people think
OL,12,Fof me, I am pretty thick-skinned,
OL,13,Fwhich I think I've had to develop over
OL,14,Fyears of playing.
OL,16,F"I just think people know Sam Tomkins
OL,17,Fthe rugby league player, but they
OL,18,Fdon't know Sam Tomkins the husband and
OL,19,Fthe dad-of-four.
