OL,6,F"Sometimes athletes get put on a
OL,7,Fpedestal, and you think that's all
OL,8,Fthey are but that's certainly not the
OL,9,Fcase."
OL,11,FSam's career as a player ended with
OL,12,Flittle fanfare befitting a player who
OL,13,Fhas achieved so much, but he said he
OL,14,Fhas made peace with that.
OL,16,F"Losing my last ever game was
OL,17,Fheartbreaking, but when I look at the
OL,18,Fbigger picture of my career I've been
OL,19,Fvery very lucky," he said.
